name: all
comments:
Sixteen subjects participated in the study (n¼ 7
[43.8%] men and n¼ 9 [56.3%] women). Median age
was 38.0 years (range, 23 47 years) and median body
mass index was 23.3 kg/m2 (range, 19.8 27.8 kg/m2).
All subjects completed the study and were included in
the pharmacokinetic, pharmacodynamic, and safety
analyses.
